reviews.text: If you want traditional sushi, stay away. There are many sushi topped with strange stuff.
One of the best bargain sushi restaurants  in Kowloon District.
Good price. The food is very decent.

Fast, cheap conveyor belt sushi place.
Fast is the key here, as they have a 30 minute time limit for dine in, which passes much more quickly than you think. The time pressure makes it hard to really enjoy your meal, especially after it seems like the wait outside for a seat is longer than the meal.
Reasonable price and food

reviews.text: 平價平民壽司，堂食經常要排隊，碟碟八蚊限食30分鐘另計加一，但外帶只是3蚊件。

平就唔太多嘢揀，不過都可以叫師傅整嘅。
呢排都少咗人排隊呀旺角嗰間
速度快，有些很新鮮，有些不熱門的菜式可能轉了很多圈都沒人選

reviews.text: อร่อยราคาโดนใจ ชิ้นละ8เหรียญฮ่องกงอิ่มสบายๆ ร้านเล็กไปนิดไปช้านี่มีต่อคิวยาว
地方方便但位窄，但食物質素比其他店好，款式多補充快
